{% extends 'VegaLiteAgent/improvement_step.jinja2' %}

{% block instructions %}
Add strategic color to highlight key insights and patterns.

# SCOPE: Color Encoding Only
Focus ONLY on:
- encoding.color (conditions, scales, schemes)

DO NOT modify:
- Title styling colors (title.subtitleColor, etc.)
- Axis titles
- Tooltips
- mark type
{% endblock %}

{% block examples %}
Highlight a key category:
```yaml
encoding:
  color:
    condition:
      test: datum.state === 'NM'
      value: '#8b0000'
    value: '#d3d3d3'
```

Highlight values above threshold:
```yaml
encoding:
  color:
    condition:
      test: datum.value > 100
      value: '#e74c3c'
    value: '#bdc3c7'
```

Use color scale:
```yaml
encoding:
  color:
    field: value
    type: quantitative
    scale:
      scheme: blues
```
{% endblock %}

